Purpose
This file turns framework state into prompt messages for AegisLM and OpenAI-style chat requests.

Linear intent
1. Render metadata pairs into one compact string.
2. Render the context history in chronological order so the model can see what happened before.
3. Render the set of completed agents so the model knows the current position in the graph.
4. Build one user message that includes the agent name, task id, metadata, completed agents, history, current payload, and agent-specific instruction.
5. Build the final OpenAI-style message list as one system message plus one user message.

